+# Step 5 Is Well Posed Because The Balanced Step-4 Dossier Leaves One Named Itinerary Repair
+
+Status: `VERIFIED` chain-step verdict with `INFERRED` dossier synthesis
+
+The completed balanced Step-4 dossier leaves one sharp outcome on the already
+frozen packet ledger.
